title: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: Exception is thrown when trying to export data from the attached report to table containing highlight/map.
OB: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from a table that contains a highlight/map in the attached report.
EB: The data should be successfully exported from the table containing a highlight/map in the attached report.
SR:
Steps to reproduce:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Navigate to the table that contains a highlight/map.
3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
4. Observe the exception that is thrown.
